snippet.title: Zooika Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out my new game, Zooika, it's coming soon on Steam! Please wish list it now! 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2994730/Zooika?utm_source=Youtube&utm_medium=Trailer

It's a suika (watermelon) style game, featuring adorable animals. There's multiple play modes, different play areas, challenges, achievements and leaderboards. 
 
I aim to release the game at the end of the year, wish list it now!!
